7,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/07\/26\/abu-darda-ilm-taalum-hilm-tahalum\/","url_meta":{"origin":39801,"position":0},"title":"Abu Darda on Learning: Knowledge, forbearance must be nurtured","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Raja\u2019 ibn Haywah reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, knowledge only comes by learning and forbearance only comes by cultivating forbearance. Whoever aims for good will receive goodness and whoever seeks to evade evil will be protected from it.\u201d Source: Rawd\u0323at al-\u02bbUqala\u0304 100 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35393,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/03\/16\/abu-darda-sabr\/","url_meta":{"origin":39801,"position":1},"title":"Abu Darda on Patience: Be forbearing in the face of insults, curses","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 16, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman ibn Jubayr reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cGive up your reputation for the sake of Allah. Whoever abuses you, insults you, or fights you, leave him to Allah. If you do a bad deed, then ask forgiveness from Allah.\u201d Source: Ta\u0304ri\u0304kh Dimashq 47\/180\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25789,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/21\/abu-darda-on-marriage-husband-and-wife-should-try-to-please-each-other\/","url_meta":{"origin":39801,"position":2},"title":"Abu Darda on Marriage: Husband and wife should try to please each other","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 21, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibrahim ibn Adham reported: Abu Darda said to his wife Umm Darda, may Allah be pleased with both of them, \u201cIf I become angry, then try to please me. If you become angry, then I will try to please you. Were we not to act this way, how quickly would\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17453,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/02\/divine-decree-providence-fate-good\/","url_meta":{"origin":39801,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Qadr: Allah only decrees goodness for believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 2, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI am amazed by the believer. Verily, Allah does not decree anything for the believers except what is good for them.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 12906 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27003,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/01\/07\/abu-darda-backbiting-loan\/","url_meta":{"origin":39801,"position":4},"title":"Abu Darda on Backbiting: Loan them your reputation until Judgment Day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Yahya ibn Sa\u2019id reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cI realized that people were like leaves with no thorns among them, but then they became thorns with no leaves among them. If you criticize them, they will criticize you. If you leave them alone, they will\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32491,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/24\/world-is-cursed-except-ikhlaas\/","url_meta":{"origin":39801,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dunya: Entire world cursed but sincerity to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe world is cursed and everything in it is cursed, except whatever seeks the countenance of Allah Almighty.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Sha\u0304miyyi\u0304n lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 602 Grade: Hasan li ghayrihi (fair due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/39801","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collectio